    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Policy_Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Access to information and information processing facilities shall be limited based on business and security requirements. A formal user access provisioning process shall be implemented.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Legal_Citation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">ISO 27001:2022 Annex A.9 - Access Control</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation_Steps__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">1. Document access control policy (A.9.1)
2. Implement user registration/de-registration (A.9.2.1)
3. Manage privileged access rights (A.9.2.3)
4. Review user access rights (A.9.2.5)
5. Implement secure log-on procedures (A.9.4.2)
6. Restrict access to program source code (A.9.4.5)</value>
    </values>
